; Regression test for issue #1054: -X COMMODITY / -V produces Adjustment entries but 'D' does not. (BZ#1054)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1054
;
; The D directive sets the default commodity but does NOT produce revaluation
; adjustment entries when prices change. Using -V or -X COMMODITY does produce
; those <Revalued> adjustment entries.

D $1.00

P 2015/01/01 STOCK $10.00
P 2015/02/01 STOCK $20.00

2015/01/01 Buy stock
    Assets:Investments    5 STOCK @ $10.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg -V -M -e 2015/03/01 Assets:Investments
15-Jan-01 - 15-Jan-31           Assets:Investments           $50.00       $50.00
15-Feb-01 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                   $50.00      $100.00
end test

test reg -X $ -M -e 2015/03/01 Assets:Investments
15-Jan-01 - 15-Jan-31           Assets:Investments           $50.00       $50.00
15-Feb-01 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                   $50.00      $100.00
end test

test reg -M -e 2015/03/01 Assets:Investments
15-Jan-01 - 15-Jan-31           Assets:Investments          5 STOCK      5 STOCK
end test
